title: Herbert W. Armstrong - Ambassador College Publications (PDF)
description:
For clarification's sake these booklets were NOT written by Herbert W. Armstrong. 

These booklets were written by ministers who worked under Mr. Armstrong at 

Ambassador College such as but not limited to:

Herman Hoeh, John Schroeder, Garner Ted Armstrong, David Jon Hill, George Johnson,

and others. Also included is a nice compendium of Mr. Armstrong's worldwide 

ministry as he faithfully served in the work of God for 53 years.



This torrent completes my final upload of every Herbert W. Armstrong PDF file I 

have. I will seed to get things going as long as I can but from there it's your 

responsibility to keep this truth alive and earnestly contend for the faith that 

was once delivered.

                                                   
                                                                    -Rastakhan
